               <p>DAVID PLANT. I am related to Mr. Thomas Plant: a <rs id="t18290611-311-viclabel1640" type="occupation">grocer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-311-victim2226 t18290611-311-viclabel1640"></join>, of <placeName id="t18290611-311-crimeloc1641">Upper Seymour-street</placeName>
