                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18290611-311-off1638 t18290611-311-crimeloc1641"></join>. A bag of rice was taken from his premises last Thursday, but I did not miss it till the officer came and told me of it - it had been on the threshold of the door.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290611-311-person2227">
                  ROBERT 
                  TEASDALE
               <interp inst="t18290611-311-person2227" type="surname" value="TEASDALE"></interp>
